PREFIX  resource:  <http://nl.dbpedia.org/resource/>

WHERE   { ?price dbpedia:birthPlace resource:Amsterdam }

SELECT ?page ?lat ?long (bif:st_distance(?geo, bif:st_point(42.883, -72.8981)))
    WHERE{
    ?m foaf:page ?page.
    ?m geo:geometry ?geo.
    ?m geo:lat ?lat.
    ?m geo:long ?long.
    FILTER (bif:st_intersects (?geo, bif:st_point(42.883, -72.8981), 300))
    }
    ORDER BY ASC 4 LIMIT 5

                SELECT ?name ?long ?lat

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> SELECT DISTINCT ?category ?label COUNT(?o) AS ?numOfInstances  WHERE { ?category rdfs:label ?label .  ?label bif:contains "'german 'and' physicists'" .  ?o dcterms:subject ?category .  FILTER (lang(?label) = 'en' || lang(?label) = '') } ORDER BY DESC(?numOfInstances) LIMIT 30

SELECT DISTINCT ?validChild ?label_child ?comment_child WHERE { ?validChild dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:German_physicists> . ?validChild rdfs:label ?label_child. FILTER (lang(?label_child) = 'en' ) OPTIONAL {  ?validChild rdfs:comment ?comment_child FILTER (lang(?comment_child) = 'en' )}} LIMIT 1000 OFFSET 0

SELECT ?type ?class ?labelOfType ?labelOfClass COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?numOfInstances WHERE {  ?s dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:German_physicists> . ?s ?type ?o . ?o dcterms:subject ?class . ?type rdfs:label ?labelOfType . ?class rdfs:label ?labelOfClass . FILTER (lang(?labelOfClass) = 'en') } ORDER BY DESC(?numOfInstances) LIMIT 40

SELECT DISTINCT ?parent ?label_parent ?comment_parent ?validChild ?label_child ?comment_child WHERE { ?parent dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:German_physicists> . ?parent <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/doctoralAdvisor> ?validChild. ?parent rdfs:label ?label_parent. FILTER (lang(?label_parent) = 'en' ) OPTIONAL {  ?parent rdfs:comment ?comment_parent FILTER (lang(?comment_parent) = 'en' )}?validChild dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:German_physicists> . ?validChild rdfs:label ?label_child. FILTER (lang(?label_child) = 'en' ) OPTIONAL {  ?validChild rdfs:comment ?comment_child FILTER (lang(?comment_child) = 'en' )}} LIMIT 1000 OFFSET 0

SELECT ?type ?class ?labelOfType ?labelOfClass COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?numOfInstances WHERE {  ?s dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:German_physicists> . ?s ?type ?o . ?o dcterms:subject ?class . ?type rdfs:label ?labelOfType . ?class rdfs:label ?labelOfClass . FILTER (lang(?labelOfClass) = 'en') } ORDER BY DESC(?numOfInstances) LIMIT 40

SELECT ?k ?depiction
    WHERE{
   
    ?m geo:geometry ?geo.
    ?m geo:lat ?lat.
    ?m geo:long ?long.
    ?m <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/thumbnail> ?thumbnail.
